# Design & Analysis of Bodywork for an Autonomous Racing Car
## MSc Dissertation — Hertfordshire Autonomous Racing (HAR) FS-AI 2026
### University of Hertfordshire | 2025–2026

## Overview
Sole engineer responsible for the complete structural 
bodywork programme for the HAR Formula Student Autonomous 
(FS-AI) 2026 race car entry. This project covers the full 
engineering cycle from material selection and concept design 
through to FEA simulation, VARI manufacturing, and physical 
test validation.

